Text:
Hi mr anonymous, just want to confirm if this app has the new Zealand map. Thanks. 

If anybody already using this app, kindly comment on the app. Thanks again.

I downloaded this and extracted the .ipa and .app to examine its contents. I do not see any .fbl map files that relate to New Zealand (or any country outside of Europe for that matter). It seems to be a compiled Europe version of iGo from all the different versions on the AppStore (Eastern, Western, UK+Ireland, etc.). The "Worldwide" moniker seems to be false. I will have to look elsewhere for the North America version.
